snippet.textDisplay: Yeah I've never understood lightner brands claiming they lighten anywhere from 4-8 levels... The level of lightness will ALWAYS depend on the level of developer used, I think it's whack of these brands to claim their lightners lighten more levels than another brand. In general it doesn't matter what brand of lightner you use, if you use the same volume of peroxide you'll get the same lift as long as the product stays moist throughtout processessing.
